🔬 Module Details
1️⃣ The Improved LSTM Model
Ablation Experiment
The ablation_experiment/ directory contains code for testing different feature combinations.

Parameter	Description
input_size_1	Feature dimension for factor group 1
input_size_2	Feature dimension for factor group 2
input_size_3	Feature dimension for factor group 3
input_size_4	Feature dimension for factor group 4

Training Module
Located in train/, includes:

Model definition
Training scripts
Loss functions
Learning rate scheduler
Model checkpoints
Dataset Groups (configured in config.py):

Group	Time Period
Group1	Baseline
Group2	2017-03-03 to 2017-09-03
Group3	2017-09-04 to 2018-03-04
Group4	2019-07-29 to 2020-01-29
Group5	2020-01-30 to 2020-07-30
Group6	2021-08-24 to 2022-02-23

Outputs:

Prediction results
Performance metrics
Confusion matrices
Trading signals
Backtesting System
Evaluates trading strategies and calculates:

Returns and cumulative curves
Maximum Drawdown
Sharpe Ratio
Performance visualizations
Traditional ML Baselines
The ML/ directory contains implementations of classical machine learning methods for comparison.


